{"id": "1430395393543376997", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 19, "author_id": "1419110621533704253", "author_name": "tuyu1ro._.1128", "author_bot": false, "content": "ダメ強のおまけでクリダメと毒もらえるの\n嬉しいな〜という感じです！", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T03:20:37.282000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["516998769888329749"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1430379106708619274", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1430396501833551943", "channel_id": "1400058619726266462", "type": 0, "author_id": "516998769888329749", "author_name": "zzzorz", "author_bot": false, "content": "クリティダメも10％くらい入るんでしたっけ！\n今見てみましたが、他のダメ強系ってメインの強化倍率そこまで高くないのですねー", "timestamp": "2025-10-22T03:25:01.519000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
